div.div:
A stand-alone general purpose cache
Currently only used to cache pom xml so we don't over-query maven repos.
Example key: ("clj-rest-client" "1.0.0-rc7")
value is nippy blob of pom xml string.

div.div:
Describes builds.
- releases describes successful builds.
- builds.error_info_map is a nippy blob of a map
representing the JVM exception, if any, for cljdoc site side
processing.

div.div:
Describes library docs.
- versions.name is the library version
- platform is clj or cljs
- versions.meta is a nippy blob of edn of a realized
version of the library's cljdoc.edn. It includes
- :config copy of library's cljdoc.edn
- :doc article attributes and content readied for rendering
- :scm includes mapping of files back to scm (ex. github)
- namespaces.meta - is nippy blob of edn for metadata for
the library's namespaces
- vars.meta - is a nippy blob of edn for metadata for
the library's vars
